title: List of Estonian football transfers winter 2021–22
text:
This is a list of <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="transfer%20%28football%29">transfers</a> in the winter transfer window 2021–22 by club.
This transfer window is open between the <a href="2021%20Meistriliiga">2021 Meistriliiga</a> and the <a href="2022%20Meistriliiga">2022 Meistriliiga</a> season. 1 club has changed: <a href="Maardu%20Linnameeskond">Maardu Linnameeskond</a> joins Estonian top division, while <a href="Viljandi%20JK%20Tulevik">Viljandi JK Tulevik</a> was relegated.
